<item>
<title>畅销27年！两代日本人，看这套书长大，有娃必买</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/MIHq0rLQNI</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/MIHq0rLQNI</guid>
<description>&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;128&quot; data-backw=&quot;578&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.2222222222222222&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;828&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OCIwxC35pAgjlicJsAHCN1MQ3wDEJfDicY5mpAu8AhXEsLS3Licxic4CnJQibUYbqLkN6wicpfkAdnUiaAzsxgx1u7bLg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;当孩子第一次拿起笔，画出七扭八拐的图案时，家长请注意：宝宝已迎来人生中想象力&amp;amp;创造力的第一个高峰——艺术敏感期。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;这一时期，伴随着对世界感知的高速进化，一颗叫做“审美”的种子在孩子心里生根。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;紧接着要进行的就是：美的教育。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;434&quot; data-backw=&quot;578&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1280&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OCIwxC35pAiaxKIeOib9a7PrbKYwbLO0OOrBxuPpibYiab1palXL94lgxNL5akCXKb0AWUdF36uOz02U9PesNDo3UQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;美学家蒋勋说：人审美水平的高低，决定了他竞争力水平。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;审美是一个人对世界的感知和创造，影响着孩子许多方面才能的习得和发挥。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;更重要的是，经历过良好美育的人，拥有变生存为生活的能力。在同等经济条件下，总能找到更有趣、更自信的生活方式。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;434&quot; data-backw=&quot;578&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;578&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;434&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1280&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OCIwxC35pAiaxKIeOib9a7PrbKYwbLO0OOOibxb6pD6nN51lJsjQuibA5NEeXkcyTRn5Pmy11BQqicRFZ1omOQuu5Xg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;道理都懂了，拿啥去抓住孩子的“艺术敏感期”进行美育呢？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;不如向隔壁日本家长取取经，用这套畅销70多万册的《你好，艺术》，和孩子一起耍。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages __bg_gif&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/OCIwxC35pAhsoJJGH5qvuqh9fGpQadicbMOJDBLL4adsMibqDULoFYl4TIGqiafPiaI8koP1RIhYTmicjq6vku0UUgw/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot; visible=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;这套书收录了&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;全球50座知名博物馆的165幅经典画作，是&lt;span&gt;“日本三大出版社之一”小学馆的“镇馆之宝”，&lt;/span&gt;十分重量级。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;对，就是梵高、毕加索、莫奈等大师的名画。什么？小孩子看不懂？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;此言差矣，不是说孩子年纪小就不懂何为美，就只能看花花绿绿、猪猪熊熊的低幼作品，他们的心远比我们想象的辽阔。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

